#

Slow-Cooked Beef Ragu with Pappardelle

$25
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

Comfort FoodItalianPastaSlow-Cooked

Description

A rich and hearty beef ragu, slow-cooked to perfection, served over wide, tender pappardelle pasta.

Ingredients

  • Beef chuck roast: 2 lbs
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Onion: 1, diced
  • Carrot: 1, diced
  • Celery: 1 stalk, diced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Crushed tomatoes: 28 oz
  • Red wine: 1 cup
  • Beef broth: 2 cups
  • Bay leaves: 2
  • Fresh thyme: 1 sprig
  • Pappardelle pasta: 12 oz
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
